{"tid":1077557,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大埔昌運238°C Bakery殘體字寫「生日快樂」賤舖終於執笠！","createTime":"2019-03-25T16:01:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-27T17:57:52.000Z","uid":79563,"like":463,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"03356568ad090780b4c70d1ac92fab83f3c92d95","tid":1077557,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T16:01:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.postimg.cc/Kz7hgKjM/238.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.postimg.cc%2FKz7hgKjM%2F238.jpg&h=40d360ed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n回帶：<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2067583/香港訂蛋糕生日牌竟寫簡體字！店員：你無講明寫繁體\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fezone.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Farticle%2F2067583%2F%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E8%A8%82%E8%9B%8B%E7%B3%95%E7%94%9F%E6%97%A5%E7%89%8C%E7%AB%9F%E5%AF%AB%E7%B0%A1%E9%AB%94%E5%AD%97%EF%BC%81%E5%BA%97%E5%93%A1%EF%BC%9A%E4%BD%A0%E7%84%A1%E8%AC%9B%E6%98%8E%E5%AF%AB%E7%B9%81%E9%AB%94&d=Fb7z1ilWoLc7MobAJ3fbq6NZBGycwMyv8OGD44uLuTw%3D&h=1cee0a09\" target=\"_blank\">https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2067583/香港訂蛋糕生日牌竟寫簡體字！店員：你無講明寫繁體</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2065000/2067583/1_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2065000%2F2067583%2F1_1024.jpg&h=b6008028&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n訂生日蛋糕加上一塊寫上祝福語（如「生日快樂」）的牌子，本來是一件簡單不過的事，不過早前一位網民卻因此嬲到震。在上星期六，這位網民到一間餅店訂蛋糕，並加錢要生日牌，不料原句「生日快樂」，卻變成簡體的「生日快乐」，令事主相當憤怒，不料店員回覆事主時竟說：「你無講明寫繁體字。」<br />\n<br />\n該名事主，稍早前在「Tai Po 大埔」facebook 群網發帖表示：「本人星期六晚去左呢間咁既餅店訂蛋糕加錢寫埋生日牌，到我今日下午去拎時，我眼都凸埋，我同店員講點解d字咁核突同寫簡體字，店員竟然答我：『你無講明寫繁體字。』當時我火都滾埋，我問佢知唔知呢度係邊度，佢答：『昌運。』我仲滾，我話呢度係香港唔係大陸，如果我要用簡體字生日牌我去深圳買喇。」同時，事主表明以後都不會再光顧這家餅店。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2065000/2067583/2_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2065000%2F2067583%2F2_600.jpg&h=3dcf06e7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n此帖發布後，惹來不少迴響。不少網民質疑，也許「乐」比「樂」易寫，師傅因偷懶而用簡體字，其他留言包括：「張單明明係正筆字，為何會變成簡體字嫁？蛋糕賣相已經不可能接受，仲要駁嘴&hellip;&hellip;比我拎個掟 9 佢啦！」、「睇到答昌運真係唔好意思笑左」、「其實錯了，講句唔好意思攪錯了，條氣都順 D，最好笑仲要將錯誤推落個客度」等。至於餅店方面，稍早發表聲明道歉，解釋：「昨日蛋糕牌事件屬第一日入職的新同事不熟悉公司運作所引致，已作出內部處分及會加緊培訓新入職同事。本公司對此事致萬二分歉意。」"},{"pid":"7f186f8cf2114a19e2432e6a4e6319cc7cc73d3a","tid":1077557,"uid":54721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T16:14:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93a1c9bd1f19362902bb799d9acf5b438e14257e","tid":1077557,"uid":165510,"like":70,"dislike":3,"score":67,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T16:22:23.000Z","msg":"讓撚返個鋪位出黎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d68259a536acdf97c5f13427b927879225987cba","tid":1077557,"uid":53026,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T16:23:16.000Z","msg":"凶舖"},{"pid":"f9af7c47320a91f7d4545675406fcf91a3906c38","tid":1077557,"uid":79563,"like":47,"dislike":7,"score":40,"quote":{"pid":"93a1c9bd1f19362902bb799d9acf5b438e14257e","tid":1077557,"uid":165510,"like":70,"dislike":3,"score":67,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T16:22:23.000Z","msg":"讓撚返個鋪位出黎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T16:24:08.000Z","msg":"你個名<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db4cc8e0d92d11141655e89fdaa12b8d3b5e7e8f","tid":1077557,"uid":165510,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"quote":{"pid":"f9af7c47320a91f7d4545675406fcf91a3906c38","tid":1077557,"uid":79563,"like":47,"dislike":7,"score":40,"quote":{"pid":"93a1c9bd1f19362902bb799d9acf5b438e14257e","tid":1077557,"uid":165510,"like":70,"dislike":3,"score":67,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T16:22:23.000Z","msg":"讓撚返個鋪位出黎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm